        "date":  "2026-07-07",
        "theme":  "Enterprise",
        "summary":  "The article identifies four foundational AI architecture elements IT leaders should prioritize to move from experimentation to production: data quality, context engineering via retrieval-augmented generation, governance with built-in observability, and preservation of human expertise. These structural components remain stable even as AI models and agentic systems continue to evolve.",
